statisticalConceptsDefinitions.EN:
Total fertilizers consumption (N+P): Different fertilizers reported are summed to obtain total fertilizers consumption.
Total fertilizers consumption is divided by Agricultural Area (Permanent crops, Arable land, and permanent pastures) to obtain Consumption in nutrients/Agricultural Area.
Indicators: 
Nitrogen Fertilizers use per arable land and permanent crop area (N tonnes / 1000 Ha);  
Phosphate Fertilizers use per arable land and permanent crop area (P205 tonnes / 1000 Ha);  
Nitrogen + Phosphate Fertilizers use per arable land and permanent crop area (N+P205 tonnes / 1000 Ha) 

