Nitrogen + Phosphate Fertilizers use per arable land and permanent crop area (N+P205 tonnes / 1000 Ha) "

"Total fertilizers consumption (N+P, N+P+K): Different fertilizers reported are summed to obtain total fertilizers consumption.                                             The indicator in EUROSTAT and OECD frameworks:  Eurostat: AEI n.5. Definition in the original frameworks: EUROSTAT: main indicator: Applications of nitrogen and phosphorus via mineral fertilizers in kg per ha per year; Supporting indicators: Total amounts of nitrogen and phosphorus applied per crop, in kg per ha per year. 
Data used in the original framework:  EUROSTAT: Farm Accountancy Data Network (FADN), FSS, European Fertilizer Manufacturers Association (EFMA). 
References:  EUROSTAT: IRENA indicator factsheet; DireDate Task 1 Report. 

 
